packages.name: Microsoft.Identity.Abstractions
packages.description: Interface for higher level API for confidential client applications.

packages.name: Microsoft.Identity.Client
packages.description: This package contains the binaries of the Microsoft Authentication Library for .NET (MSAL.NET).

packages.name: Microsoft.Identity.Client.Broker
packages.description: This package contains binaries needed to use brokers in public client desktop applications and supersedes Microsoft.Identity.Client.Desktop.

packages.name: Microsoft.Identity.Client.Extensions.Msal
packages.description: This package contains the public client (desktop) caching to Microsoft Authentication Library for .NET (MSAL.NET)

packages.name: Microsoft.Identity.Client.NativeInterop
packages.description: This package contains binaries needed to use brokers in public client desktop applications.

packages.name: Microsoft.IdentityModel.Abstractions
packages.description: A package containing thin abstractions for Microsoft.IdentityModel.

packages.name: Microsoft.IdentityModel.JsonWebTokens
packages.description: Includes types that provide support for creating, serializing and validating JSON Web Tokens.

packages.name: Microsoft.IdentityModel.Logging
packages.description: Includes Event Source based logging support.

packages.name: Microsoft.IdentityModel.Tokens
packages.description: Includes types that provide support for SecurityTokens, Cryptographic operations: Signing, Verifying Signatures, Encryption.

packages.name: System.IdentityModel.Tokens.Jwt
packages.description: Includes types that provide support for creating, serializing and validating JSON Web Tokens. As of IdentityModel 7x, this is a legacy tool that should be replaced with Microsoft.IdentityModel.JsonWebTokens.
